OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776881466
OL,3,CKirkstone Pass landslide repairs start
OL,5,FWork to repair the Kirkstone Pass on
OL,6,Fthe A592 at High Kingate following a
OL,7,Fsignificant landslide has started.
OL,9,FThe road between Troutbeck and the
OL,10,FKirkstone Inn has been closed since
OL,11,FNovember when bad weather caused a
OL,12,Fhuge landslip, which partly undermined
OL,13,Fthe carriageway.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
