OL,3,CKirkstone Pass landslide repairs start
OL,5,FEmergency procurement processes were
OL,6,Fused to bring in expert ground
OL,7,Finvestigation teams, and surveys of
OL,8,Fthe carriageway and steep banking
OL,9,Fstarted before Christmas, to determine
OL,10,Fthe best repair.
OL,12,FVarious options were considered,
OL,13,Fincluding carriageway realignment and
OL,14,Fbuilding a tiered concrete retaining
OL,15,Fwall.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
