OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776881466
OL,3,CKirkstone Pass landslide repairs start
OL,5,FThe council says the agreed works are
OL,6,Fdesigned to protect the landscape as
OL,7,Fwell as improving the stability of the
OL,8,Fsteep slope, protecting the highway
OL,9,Fand reducing the risk of future damage
OL,10,Fand landslips.
OL,12,FNow specialist contractors are on site
OL,13,Fstarting the repair and reinstatement
OL,14,Fworks, which include:
OL,16,FIt is expected to take 12 weeks. The
OL,17,Fcouncil hopes to re-open the important
OL,18,FLake District road before the start of
OL,19,Fthe main school holidays in July and
OL,20,Fpeak summer season for tourists.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
