PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1776881466
OL,3,CKirkstone Pass landslide repairs start
OL,5,FCouncillor Peter Thornton said: "It is
OL,6,Fa very well used route, both for local
OL,7,Ftraffic and with tourists accessing
OL,8,FKirkstone Pass and the wonderful
OL,9,Fattractions in the Ullswater Valley."
OL,11,F"Local parish councils and businesses
OL,12,Fhave been kept updated on the landslip
OL,13,Frepair process and the council has
OL,14,Fworked with Cumbria Tourism to help
OL,15,Fpromote the message that areas around
OL,16,Fthe closure have still been accessible
OL,17,Fand 'open for business'," he added.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
